<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٥٢- يَوْمَئِذٍ يَتَّبِعُونَ الدَّاعِيَ لا عِوَجَ لَهُ وَخَشَعَتِ الْأَصْواتُ لِلرَّحْمنِ فَلا تَسْمَعُ إِلَّا هَمْساً <span class="c2">(١٠٨)</span> <span class="c2">«١»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٥٣-* وَأَوْحَيْنا إِلى مُوسى أَنْ أَسْرِ بِعِبادِي إِنَّكُمْ مُتَّبَعُونَ <span class="c2">(٥٢)</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>فَأَرْسَلَ فِرْعَوْنُ فِي الْمَدائِنِ حاشِرِينَ <span class="c2">(٥٣)</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>إِنَّ هؤُلاءِ لَشِرْذِمَةٌ قَلِيلُونَ <span class="c2">(٥٤)</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>وَإِنَّهُمْ لَنا لَغائِظُونَ <span class="c2">(٥٥)</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>وَإِنَّا لَجَمِيعٌ حاذِرُونَ <span class="c2">(٥٦)</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>فَأَخْرَجْناهُمْ مِنْ جَنَّاتٍ وَعُيُونٍ <span class="c2">(٥٧)</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>وَكُنُوزٍ وَمَقامٍ كَرِيمٍ <span class="c2">(٥٨)</span><a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>كَذلِكَ وَأَوْرَثْناها بَنِي إِسْرائِيلَ <span class="c2">(٥٩)</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>فَأَتْبَعُوهُمْ مُشْرِقِينَ <span class="c2">(٦٠)</span> <span class="c2">«٢»</span><a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>٥٤- قُلْ فَأْتُوا بِكِتابٍ مِنْ عِنْدِ اللَّهِ هُوَ أَهْدى مِنْهُما أَتَّبِعْهُ إِنْ كُنْتُمْ صادِقِينَ <span class="c2">(٤٩)</span><a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>فَإِنْ لَمْ يَسْتَجِيبُوا لَكَ فَاعْلَمْ أَنَّما يَتَّبِعُونَ أَهْواءَهُمْ وَمَنْ أَضَلُّ مِمَّنِ اتَّبَعَ هَواهُ بِغَيْرِ هُدىً مِنَ اللَّهِ إِنَّ اللَّهَ لا يَهْدِي الْقَوْمَ الظَّالِمِينَ <span class="c2">(٥٠)</span> <span class="c2">«٣»</span><a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>٥٥- فَدَعا رَبَّهُ أَنَّ هؤُلاءِ قَوْمٌ مُجْرِمُونَ <span class="c2">(٢٢)</span><a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>فَأَسْرِ بِعِبادِي لَيْلًا إِنَّكُمْ مُتَّبَعُونَ <span class="c2">(٢٣)</span> <span class="c2">«٤»</span><a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>٥٦- يَوْمَ تَرْجُفُ الرَّاجِفَةُ <span class="c2">(٦)</span><a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>تَتْبَعُهَا الرَّادِفَةُ <span class="c2">(٧)</span><a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>قُلُوبٌ يَوْمَئِذٍ واجِفَةٌ <span class="c2">(٨)</span><a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>أَبْصارُها خاشِعَةٌ <span class="c2">(٩)</span> <span class="c2">«٥»</span><a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
